<main>
  
  <input id="tab1" type="radio" name="tabs" checked>
  <label for="tab1"><a href="/steps">Step 1</a></label>
    
  <input id="tab2" type="radio" name="tabs">
  <label for="tab2"><a href="/posts/new">Step 2</a></label>
    
  <input id="tab3" type="radio" name="tabs">
  <label for="tab3"><a href="/posts/objects">Step 3</a></label>
    
  <input id="tab4" type="radio" name="tabs">
  <label for="tab4"><a href="/posts/:id/preview">Step 4</a></label>

  <input id="tab5" type="radio" name="tabs">
  <label for="tab5"><a href="/posts/:id/preview">Step 5</a></label>
    
  <section id= "dashboard">
  	<div class="aim">
  		Our aim of this step is to generate a stream key from facebook so that we can use it to stream video on your page. 
  	</div>
	<div id="division">
	<p id="text">1. Click the <a id="liveButton" class="fb_button">New Post</a> button and login to your facebook account. Select <strong>"Share on a page you manage"</strong> option from the options provided and then click the next button. <strong>Come back to us for furthur instructions!</strong></p>
	<%= image_tag "step_1_2.jpg" ,:class => "step_image"%>
	</div>

	<div id="empty"></div>

  <div id="division">
  <p id="text" class="stext">2. If your browser blocks pop ups from our site, allow them as shown in figure and click 'Finished' button and <strong>start again from Step 1.</strong></p>
  <%= image_tag "step_1_3.jpg" ,:class => "step_image"%>
  </div>

  <div id="empty"></div>

	<div id="division">
	<p id="text" class="stext">3. A new screen will pop up showing information regarding the video. Copy the <strong>STREAM KEY</strong> and give it to us in Step 2. <strong>Come again for next instruction.</strong></p>
	<%= image_tag "step_1_4.jpg" ,:class => "step_image"%>
	</div>

  <div id="empty"></div>

  <div id="division">
  <p id="text" class="stext">4. Go to settings and click the embed option as shown in picture.</p>
  <%= image_tag "step_1_5.jpg" ,:class => "step_image"%>
  </div>

  <div id="empty"></div>
  
  <div id="division">
  <p id="text" class="stext">5. Copy <strong> embed video link </strong> and give it to us in Step 2.</p>
  <%= image_tag "step_1_6.jpg" ,:class => "step_image"%>
  </div>

  <div class="alert"> Do not close the facebook window </div>
	</section>

	<div class="nextpost">
	 <%= link_to 'NEXT', new_post_path%>
	</div>

	
</main>
<script>
document.getElementById('liveButton').onclick = function() {
  FB.ui({
    display: 'popup',
    method: 'live_broadcast',
    phase: 'create',
}, function(response) {
    if (!response.id) {
      alert('dialog canceled');
      return;
    }
    //alert('stream url:' + response.secure_stream_url);
    FB.ui({
      display: 'popup',
      method: 'live_broadcast',
      phase: 'publish',
      broadcast_data: response,
    }, function(response) {
    });
  });
};
</script>

